Fans of Marvel&#8217; &#8220;Luke Cage&#8221; can rest easy: Netflix has announced plans to renew the show for a second season.The streaming service delivered the news on the show&#8217;s social media pages Sunday, with a &#8220;Season 2 Coming Soon&#8221; announcement in fluorescent lights set against a barber&#8217;s shop.In the show, Mike Colter plays the bulletproof hero Luke Cage. The show&#8217;s first season also starred Rosario Dawson, Mahershala Ali, Simone Missick, Theo Rossi, and Alfre Woodard.-Relaxnews